c + o = u
n + o = t
L + i = n  // 15

Mouth + One = Monkey
Lake + Monkey = Monkey Island

6 - Chum: 
Water + Water = Lake
Earth + Earth = Mountain
Mountain + O = Mouth
Lake + Mouth = Fish
Fish + Fish = Shark
Mouth + Shark = Chum

6 - Cayenne Pepper: 
Water + Water = Lake
Fire + Water = Steam
Steam + Wine = Stew
Fire + Stew = Chili
Chili + Lake = Cayenne
Cayenne + O = Cayenne Pepper

6 - Lolamont: 
Water + Water = Lake
Lake + Plant = Lily
Earth + Earth = Mountain
Lake + O = Olake
Lily + Olake = Lola
Lola + Mountain = Lolamont

6 - Hellebore: 
Water + Water = Lake
Lake + Plant = Lily
Earth + Earth = Mountain
Mountain + Number = 8
8 + O = H
H + Lily = Hellebore
